{"tid":681523,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"CUHK Secrets: 點解學生會派代表出席來歷不明嘅學獨聯集會？","createTime":"2018-05-28T06:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T06:26:42.000Z","uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8258efec8a3c795d5946c0ffbb5e948ce8ac1c77","tid":681523,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#CU1278<br />\n&quot;請問一下凌霜，點解你地出facebook post，派代表(副會長同常務幹事)出席學生獨立聯盟既旺角集會？個組織來歷不明，係人係鬼都唔知。仲話有興趣的同學可一同出席。你地有冇查證學生獨立聯盟的背景？<br />\n<br />\n煩請凌霜解釋你們和學生獨立聯盟之間的關係！<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n學生獨立聯盟口號為：「香港獨立，以死相搏」；<br />\n轉個頭留言： 「點解警察要害怕手無寸鐵嘅學生」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CUHKSecrets/posts/1526200890817354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCUHKSecrets%2Fposts%2F1526200890817354&d=dkh7bE%2B2t6lWSyqp9%2BsDuKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=95ba3d7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CUHKSecrets/posts/1526200890817354</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}